description: Commands to view executions of a Container App Job.

commands.name: az containerapp job execution list
commands.summary: Get list of all executions of a Container App Job.
examples: az containerapp job execution list -n my-containerapp-job -g MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az containerapp job execution show
commands.summary: Get execution of a Container App Job.
examples: az containerapp job execution show -n my-containerapp-job -g MyResourceGroup --job-execution-name MyContainerAppJob-66v9xh0
